-- State Farm Appoints Former Suncorp-Metway CEO Jones to Board of Directors
-- Hugh Son
-- 2010-06-15T15:03:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-15/state-farm-appoints-former-suncorp-metway-ceo-jones-to-board-of-directors.html

          
          
             State Farm Mutual Automobile
Insurance Co. named W. Steven Jones, former chief executive
officer of Australia’s Suncorp-Metway Ltd., to the company’s
board of directors.  
 Jones is a professor at the University of North Carolina’s
Kenan-Flagler Business School, according to a Business Wire
statement today from Bloomington, Illinois-based State Farm, the
largest U.S. home and auto insurer.  
